name: Gods [SG]
description:
Gods is an arcade-platformer game developed by The Bitmap Brothers and Bitmap Brothers, The. It was originally released in 1991. MINDSCAPE published the game. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
You can play Gods on Game Boy Advance, Atari ST, SNES and Commodore / Amiga.
Nation 12 scored the game.
